msgid "Hide Invisible Objects:"
msgstr "Unsichtbare Objekte ausblenden:"

#: templates/config_form.html:199
msgid ""
"If checked, objects that are geometrically impossible to see will be hidden "
"from the main list by default. They will still appear if you specifically "
"search for them."
